        To change the visibility of an event, use the <a href="../../list-of-windows/alvao-webapp/requests/request">Request</a> - <strong>Communications - Event Menu - ... </strong>- <a href="../../list-of-windows/alvao-webapp/diary/edit">Edit</a> - <strong>Show to requester</strong> tab.
    </p>

